      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a car to get you from A to B with some TLC? This vehicle is being offered at a great price for someone ready to put in a little work! While it shows significant wear and will require mechanical and cosmetic attention, it\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to own this model at a fraction of the usual cost. Perfect for a mechanic's special or a dedicated restorer!",
