      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a pristine exterior and an interior that remains in showroom state. Meticulously inspected and preserved, it offers a rare opportunity for the individual who demands nothing less than absolute excellence. This is a benchmark example of automotive preservation, ready for immediate acquisition.",
