    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this ride is. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and babied since day one. It looks and feels brand new\u2014seriously, not a single scratch or dent to be found! If you've been looking for that perfect, showroom-quality car, this is definitely the one. Come take a look and see for yourself, you're going to absolutely fall in love!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Alpine White. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, it boasts a reinforced rear subframe, a recently overhauled VANOS system, and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with zero bushing deflection, and the engine exhibits a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Every body panel retains its original VIN sticker, and the interior shows no bolster wear or pixel degradation. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Clean title. Garage kept. Single owner. No mechanical issues. Full service history included.",
      "price": 44000.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a used car; it\u2019s a time capsule. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014no rock chips, no swirl marks, and certainly no dents. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen a winter road. Inside, the cabin still carries that fresh, new-car scent. The premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the carpets are protected by original factory mats, and every piece of technology, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive cruise control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete, meticulously documented service history from the local dealership, recently underwent a comprehensive multi-point inspection, and sits on a fresh set of premium Michelin tires. If you are looking for a collector-grade example that requires absolutely zero investment or apology, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
